ComicInfo.Summary:
Calie and Violet may finally have the upper hand in the fight against wonderland as each begins accessing the mysterious 'waking dream' powers that are now at their disposal. But the Dark Cheshire and the new Mad Hatter don't plan on making things easy for them as they begin to close in. Will Calie and Violet master their new powers in time to put an end to the deadly duos rampage or will their inexperience make them their latest victims?
